snippet.title: Way of the Hunter | Lintukoto Reserve DLC Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Lintukoto Reserve DLC for Way of the Hunter is OUT NOW on PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S.

Explore the enchanting beauty of Lintukoto Reserve, from winding rivers to dense forests, and encounter a variety of unique wildlife like the Lynx and Arctic Fox.
